  <item>
    <title>gradle</title>
    <link>http://lumiere.ens.fr/~guerry/20221215113524-java_development.html#org48c46ca</link>
    <author>7696122 at gmail dot com (nil)</author>
    <guid isPermaLink="false">http://lumiere.ens.fr/~guerry/20221215113524-java_development.html#org48c46ca</guid>
    <pubDate>Sun, 25 Dec 2022 06:42:00 +0900</pubDate>

    <description><![CDATA[<p>
    gradlew를 사용하려면 gradle이 있어야 하더라
    </p>

    <div class="org-src-container">
    <pre class="src src-sh">tree ~/Works/lfcp-nxapi/gradle
    </pre>
    </div>

    <pre class="example">
    ./gradle
    └── wrapper
    └── gradle-wrapper.properties

    1 directory, 2 files
    </pre>


    <p>
    <code>gradle-wrapper.jar</code> 가 없다면 아래 명령어로 설치
    </p>

    <div class="org-src-container">
    <pre class="src src-shell">gradle wrapper
    </pre>
    </div>

    <div class="org-src-container">
    <pre class="src src-shell">tree ~/Works/lfcp-nxapi/gradle
    </pre>
    </div>

    <pre class="example">
    ./gradle
    └── wrapper
    ├── gradle-wrapper.jar
    └── gradle-wrapper.properties

    1 directory, 2 files
    </pre>
    ]]></description>
  </item>
